other_tests.findings: Increased uptake in L5/S1 and incidental diffuse bilateral increased renal uptake of Tc-99m MDP.
other_tests.changes_over_time: Resolution of the increased renal uptake was noted after cessation of NSAIDs.

other_tests.findings: Creatinine was elevated at 230 mmol/L compared to 119 mmol/L 2 months previously.
other_tests.changes_over_time: Creatinine normalized over 48 hours after withdrawal of NSAIDs, but there was a transient rise after inadvertent administration of ketorolac.
